data.description: Great, quiet and peaceful, updated and well maintained, ready to move into a home that sits on 2 acres in the Cache school district. 5 bedrooms 2 baths.  Master bedroom with full bath and walk-in closet. 2 large family sized living areas. Big kitchen with new dishwasher and new industrial microwave. Brand new AC and furnace. Two hot water heaters. All appliances stay. Backyard has a big patio. Storage shed on the property Also has a generator hook up. This beautiful property will not last long. For a private viewing call Nikki Henderson at 580-647-1663.
